        "subject": "LU-657 test: increase file stripe count for run_dd.sh",
        "message": "LU-657 test: increase file stripe count for run_dd.sh\n\nin recovery-mds-scale.sh, the clien load run_dd.sh will write\n3.8G (1,000,000 * 4096), and the OSTSIZE is just 4G, and if\nthere are some other disk consumption, it will have no disk space\nto use and cause -ENOSPC error.\n\nTest-Parameters: fortestonly envdefinitions=SLOW=yes clientcount=4 osscount=2 mdscount=2 austeroptions=-R failover=true useiscsi=true testlist=recovery-mds-scale\nSigned-off-by: Hongchao Zhang <hongchao.zhang@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: Id3222e30565d202c8b51c9c5da1553f5e8a6c81a\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
